name: Erica Nash
description: Hi, my name is Josephine, I have no children. . I don’t sleep around so I am disease free. I’m a pretty easy going person n go with the flow of things. I am the only child of my parent. My family n friends are my life. I love to read, draw, photography, pretty much anything to do with art, I love going on nature walks. If there is anything else that u would like to know about me just message me. I am tired of guys saying things that they don’t mean. If u don’t mean it than dont say it. If ur looking for a one night stand or a piece of a** sorry but I’m not that girl. I’m the girl that wants more (a meaningful relationship). I don’t care about the materialistic things. What matters to me is that u treat me good n r open n talk to me. Don’t be a coward to say what’s on ur mind or how u feel. If u can’t do that than why the hell r u looking for a girlfriend.
